* Semantic HTML only
* One H1 per page
* Unique metadata (title & description) from `/seo/metadata.ts`
* JSON‚ÄëLD Organization schema in layout
* `next/image` usage with meaningful alt text
* Canonical URLs
* Mobile‚Äëfirst responsive
* Include sitemap.ts and robots.ts

