## üß† **Component‚ÄëFirst Architecture**

All pages must be built with modular components in `components/sections/`. Example structure:

```
components/
  sections/
    HomeHero.tsx
    WhyChooseUs.tsx
    Clients.tsx
    AboutCompany.tsx
    DirectorSection.tsx
    SolutionsList.tsx
    ContactForm.tsx
    MapSection.tsx
  layout/
    Header.tsx
    Footer.tsx
```

Pages should *compose* these components only.

